title: Google Workspace
description: Google Workspace and Google for Education Deployment.
author: Mwangilwa Zimba

body.raw:
I will help you deploy Google Workspace remotely or on-premise.
Proving my ability to complete common workplace activities using cloud-based tools to create and 
share documents, spreadsheets, presentations, and files. I will demonstrate that you can communicate 
effectively with email and online meeting solutions powered by Google Cloud.
